"* The hosted class for the claims tour (see main.qn): tiny methods shaped to
"* build claim trees — hold an object while sleeping, hold it while running a
"* caller block (which may call other objects), mint siblings.
Node <- { |@n|
    init -> { @n = 0 }
    mate -> { Node.new }
    double: -> { |n| n * 2 }
    slow: -> { |ms| Async.sleep:ms; ms }
    hold:then: -> { |ms blk| Async.sleep:ms; blk.value:0 }
}
